---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Blockquote from "../components/Blockquote.astro";
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
---

<Layout
        title="About · Ethan Hann"
        description="About."
>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
        Software engineer, tech leader, and part-time farmer.
    </p>

    <p>
        Principal software engineer with 18+ years of experience leading teams and building scalable
        platforms across marketing SaaS, ad tech, and healthcare. My work centers on technical
        leadership, cloud architecture on Azure and AWS, and agile product development.
    </p>

    <p>
        I care about mentoring engineers, solving hard problems under pressure, and shipping reliable,
        maintainable software that delivers real value. I work hands-on across backend systems, cloud
        infrastructure, and AI-driven features, and I do my best work in collaborative teams that value
        autonomy, clarity, and impact.
    </p>

    <h2>Working with me</h2>

    <p>
        I'm selectively available for consulting or an FTE role if it is the right fit.
    </p>

    <p>
        Hit me up on {' '}
        <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ethanhann/">LinkedIn</Link>
    </p>


    <h2>What I've done</h2>

    <p>
        Web applications and platforms across several industries.
    </p>

    <div class="mx-6 my-4">
        <ul>
            <li>Multiple SaaS products</li>
            <li>React, Angular, Vue frontends</li>
            <li>Rust/Axum, Go/Gin, Python/Django, C#/ASP.NET, PHP/Laravel/Symfony backends</li>
            <li>Multi-region high volume API and distributed caching systems</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>
        Data and machine learning pipelines.
    </p>

    <div class="mx-6 my-4">
        <ul>
            <li>Agentic LLM pipelines</li>
            <li>Parallel processing pipelines</li>
            <li>Streaming analytics pipelines</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>
        A few things beyond the usual product work.
    </p>

    <div class="mx-6 my-4">
        <ul>
            <li>Drupal and Wordpress content-driven websites</li>
            <li>Commercial video game development libraries</li>
            <li>Various open source projects</li>
        </ul>
    </div>


    <h2>Languages I've used</h2>

    <p>
        I've written a <span class="highlight-text">significant amount</span> of Rust, Python, JavaScript, TypeScript,
        C#, and PHP.
    </p>

    <p>
        I've dabbled in Go, Java, C, and C++.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>
            <Link href="https://github.com/ethanhann">GitHub</Link>
        </li>
        <li>
            <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ethanhann/">LinkedIn</Link>
        </li>
    </ul>
</Layout>
